{"tid":1285871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"致科大學生會: 公開會議都唔可以接受","createTime":"2019-07-04T17:07:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T20:39:29.000Z","uid":157762,"like":620,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"779bcbb95e481b3d045c7e547a0ea65975da9aa5","tid":1285871,"uid":157762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:07:28.000Z","msg":"好簡單<br />\n1. 記住你嘅對手係極權政府 柒婆同你傾完之後大可以反口覆舌 <br />\n2. 我地嘅訴求可以話係冇妥協嘅餘地 唔通叫佢地放十個告兩個 唔通叫佢地唔好追究犯左法嘅黑警咁樣？呢d係由人類良知畫出嚟嘅底線 邊有得妥協？既然冇得妥協 傾嚟做乜鳩？<br />\n3. 今次係千載難逢嘅機會 難得衝完 我地仲有民意基礎 加上有美帝撐腰 我地要谷盡佢 爭取雙普選 任何形式嘅妥協都好似門前兩碼飛機一樣咁on9"},{"pid":"d6af7eed882eba93c65877c48944e18711ba89f5","tid":1285871,"uid":157762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:11:48.000Z","msg":"我要搵律師"},{"pid":"cf07cc25dac10d5c86414a81766078f88c65ea08","tid":1285871,"uid":157762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:12:27.000Z","msg":"我要投訴你"},{"pid":"eb6378069f4a90b6e97b8399a444b5131d0eeb16","tid":1285871,"uid":157762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:13:03.000Z","msg":"我要飲水"},{"pid":"6f2284d3804480a9c7332e1c476b1364be68ec5c","tid":1285871,"uid":157762,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:13:33.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"8911c1d8ef96f15d439f110171d8d8c9a14a7c61","tid":1285871,"uid":4496,"like":81,"dislike":1,"score":80,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:13:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇野好傾<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求相當清晰<br />\n香港人已經冇退讓既餘地</span></span>"},{"pid":"53d5c8e85571393b472f5c8037dec41c4e80983f","tid":1285871,"uid":19557,"like":11,"dislike":5,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:14:27.000Z","msg":"公開會議都得 5大訴求要全部要接受"},{"pid":"d8ddf4b5fd33b215079e30dd223efbdbfc7edebb","tid":1285871,"uid":157762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:14:34.000Z","msg":"我唔舒服 要去醫院"},{"pid":"f16ab8666502e38508f733011d8d01ffb8fe665e","tid":